{"root":{"data":{"id":"dhhroityrhc0","created":1775041454395,"text":"抖音团购差评处理"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhhroz13rrk0","created":1775041489655,"text":"1.普删：68/条，底线价格58/条2.强删：350","layout_mind_offset":{"x":-1.9999999403953552,"y":-139.99999582767504},"color":"#ff0000"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhhrq0ulx280","created":1775041571980,"text":"客户问会不会违规：我们最近一直在使用这种方式，没有出现过任何违规的情况！","layout_mind_offset":{"x":5.6666660341956,"y":-110.6666636996801}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhhrr1wtocw0","created":1775041652655,"text":"（不问别说）处理方式：1.申诉方式（申诉只有两次机会如果两次机会用完了就不能申诉了）2.强删","layout_mind_offset":{"x":958.4999741166839,"y":26.999997407198464}},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhhrs5d2kyo0","created":1775041738532,"text":"不用补偿","layout_mind_offset":{"x":592.4999587982915,"y":69.99999513228761}},"children":[]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}